{"type": "article", "id": 54729, "title": "霸王龙造型的台灯，可以按你的喜好凹造型｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-28T23:22:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51430, "name": "Bigrep"}, {"id": 51431, "name": "KOMONO"}, {"id": 51432, "name": "Buzzispace"}, {"id": 51433, "name": "udnDesign"}, {"id": 51434, "name": "Arman Zamani"}, {"id": 51435, "name": "July Londono"}, {"id": 51436, "name": "Cory Grosser"}, {"id": 51437, "name": "Simon Schuster"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 181, "image": "img/article/article_show/2018062821302114QTl5nkoYimSy9a.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>STRöM by Simon Schuster</h3><p>相较于充电宝刚刚进入大众市场时，近几年它们在形状、大小等方面都有了不少创新。比如设计师 Simon Schuster 设计的这款名为 STRöM 的充电宝，就直观展示了一个甜甜圈的样式，毫无疑问，它突破了大多数人对充电宝结构的想象。</p><p>整个充电宝分为两部分，一半的“甜甜圈”可以顺着铰链旋转，露出两个充电端口，在不使用时可以整齐地隐藏起来。外圈有 5 个 LED 指示灯，用来提醒用户电池电量。为了增强其便携性，设计师还设计了一个橡胶提手，希望给你的充电体验带去一丝丝幽默感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213113by3Gr6KwXBDxaNCg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760952\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806282131130GsYof1nJU8lPgiu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213113M7hHzrUNdiVEg6kx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213114eWA0OsjP1FEKI79N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806282131149BxYZU4RMdPyhO1A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806282131147XhCU3rw4ciN6xOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/06/28/a-power-bank-for-donut-lovers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Raptor Lamp 2.0 by udnDesign</h3><p>喜欢侏罗纪公园的人不少，如果想要在家中创造专属于自己的侏罗纪公园，这款霸王龙台灯是个好道具。它除了可照明之外，最大特点即在于它具有专利支撑点设计，透过整体 8 个转轴点，可以让头部、躯干与四肢左右摆动或变换姿势，调整至个人喜欢的角度，让灯具不仅是灯具，还能有互动与张力。</p><p>产品具有下颚发光和舌部发光两个光源，下颚咬合与头部的特定轴向旋转，让它兼具照明微调与真实感。灯具底部还有手机座。目前，霸王龙台灯 2.0 版本在众筹网站 Indiegogo 的早鸟价为 119 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/raptor-lamp-2-0-led-light-in-jurassic-style-family-design?utm_source=Yanko_Design&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=1806_raptor_lamp#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213217gPkT3LvMRUE06scy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213217EzXJ873TQFRwS20y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213218MvQbGDEu2as9dPVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213218ocpPJOgxN1qBKYDr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213218yQkZ1BE7rvqXa0m6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760952\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213218NZrckfxznF97BMpO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.570476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213219masoPFBtZj0Tn4RD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BuzziMood by Cory Grosser for Buzzispace</h3><p>比利时品牌 Buzzispace 成立于 2007 年，专注于办公环境的改善，既有对美学的探索，也有对噪音的控制，比如最近推出的新品 BuzziMood。</p><p>这是一款降噪墙，提出这一解决方案的是美国设计师 Cory Grosser，决定用有机的方式解决很久以来的噪音问题。BuzziMood 的主要材料是保存下来的驯鹿苔，因为对水的需求量极低，所以很好维护。</p><p>很多研究都提出，绿色可以增强工作一族的愉悦感，BuzziMood 就像它的名字所暗示的那样，希望通过柔和的绿色外观和有趣的几何形状提供更加轻松的环境。当然它更核心的功能在于吸音降噪。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213326aSAiI0y7YPeEmK3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213326TBHobunhciVr9FOa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213326ZG9rYQ8aXtmKiwUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213327InJH2hCpyzfo7SLB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497656\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213327zjO0ZKDQhxC3bW51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667969\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/buzzimood-brings-nature-to-acoustical-wall-solutions/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Homewear by July Londono</h3><p>还记得户外探险者常穿的那种拉链工装裤吗？今年刚毕业于帕森斯设计学院的设计师 July Londono 以此为灵感，将这种复杂的衣服改造为家居饰品。</p><p>这个创新系列被称为 Homewear，包括一个可用作浴巾、浴帘以及枕套的睡衣套装，一个可以变成桌布的格子棉外套等等。她试图探索服装与家居饰品之间的形态转换，算是一次趣味十足的设计实验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213413RjiGENzay2pCghF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213413QftqJEzkn9cSNWlo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018062821341491JtN0UzLVMmr5EK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213414nSUc8ClxKErPbesB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213415oYhCGA05b392Xdt7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213416XwNzZIgidCmUqsD5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213417yHEA2cX1hMl49VZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051200\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.surfacemag.com/articles/summery-checked-tablecloth-also-jacket/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Surfacemag</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Kyoto Timepiece by Arman Zamani for KOMONO</h3><p>小众腕表品牌 KOMONO 成立于比利时，由两位欧洲设计师创立。 但 KOMONO 这个词却来源于日语，意为“小东西”，“小物件”的意思。</p><p>最近它们除了一款新品 Kyoto Timepiece，出自设计师 Arman Zamani 之手，灵感来源于日式禅宗园林，类似于 KARESANSUI ，就是“枯山水”，所谓枯山水，据说这样的庭院常被用于参禅冥想。一圈圈波浪纹理和沙色，和克制的灰色系时针、分针，也符合 KOMONO 品牌的简约设计语言。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213502cWwEYzGv1NJ8U4xT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213502wzl8DduCvUAYQNfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806282135023hjrG2m5Q7qdg90O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213502w06jR41uiUZhysF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Smart Concrete Wall by NOWlab</h3><p>德国 3D 打印制造商 Bigrep 的创新实验室 NOWlab，推出了号称是全球第一款智能混凝土墙壁，将数字设计与数字制造结合在一起。它由 3D 打印模板制作而成，通过混凝土结构中的嵌入式电容传感器制成可适应表面。</p><p>它可以演变为感应式可适应混凝土屏风，墙壁的感应部分可以通过用手触碰外表面激活。屏风内置有一个传感器，设计者将六角形灯具嵌入到混凝土墙壁的六角形空隙中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533wa3QKI025XOz7lxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533d6yz8xn5COj3NETP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533jbCqUfRaF4lTDAme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533Lxz4EKk8rqU3Spej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533TNxrb2VX9izyeRlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180628213533AUN7fXTKLI8qbxuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/architecture/smart-concrete-wall-nowlab-bigrep-3d-printing-06-27-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}